snippet.title: Codename Eagle - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Codename Eagle is a computer game developed by Stockholm-based studio Refraction Games and was released in November 1999. Refraction Games later merged with EA Digital Illusions CE (DICE) and developed Battlefield 1942

This game was from 1999 and made by dice. This is the official trailer to advertise the single player side of the game. The game did very well as a multiplayer game.

Youtube messed up the sound sync..I tried to re-up but it still doesnt sync, the video I have is sync'd.
